{
  "texts": [
    "To analyze the current political situation regarding the use of AI, making the suggestion to invest as soon as possible in the development of social guidelines, public policies and educational initiatives to avoid the affluence of misinformation and propaganda generated by AI.",
    "GPT-3 shows strengths in the generation of text that precisely emulates interactive, informative and influential content that could be used to radicalize people towards far right-wing ideologies and violent behaviors.",
    "Researchers and service providers might consider contributing and investing in educational programs on the use of AI targeting mass audiences.",
    "To propose solutions to prevent undesirable social biases when GPT-3 is used for storytelling.",
    "The language models generate different occupations and levels of respect for different genders, races and sexual orientations."
  ]
}